== Amashuri yize ==
Liza Kamikazi yize muri [[Kaminuza y'u Rwanda]] i Huye mu ishami ry'itangazamakuru aho yakuye impamyabumenyi y'icyiciro cya kabiri cya kaminuza mu ishami ry' itangazamakuru.<ref>https://inyarwanda.com/inkuru/66058/urutonde-rw-abaririmbyi-20-b-abanyarwanda-babashije-kwigonde-66058.html</ref>

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Kamikazi ni umubyeyi w'abana batatu akaba afite umugabo bahuriye mu mwuga w'ubuhanzi aho uwo mugabo yatangiye amufasha mu miririmbire gusa amwigisha uko aririmba neza ariko biza kuvamo urukundo baza kubaka umuryango.<ref>https://www.kigalitoday.com/imyidagaduro/muzika/article/umuziki-wampaye-umugabo-sinawureka-liza-kamikazi</ref> Liza yaje kwegurira ubuzima bwe Yesu Kristo arakizwa yinjira mukuririmba indirimbo zihimbaza Imana.<ref>https://agakiza.org/Ubuhamya-Nyuma-yo-kwiyegurira-Kristo-Liza-Kamikazi-aratekanye.html</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Liza yatangiye umwuga w'ubuhanzi mu myaka 17 ishize aho yatangiye aririmba indirimbo zisanzwe zakunzwe cyane , amaze gukizwa nibwo yatangiye kuririmba indirimbo zihimbaza Imana nazo zakunzwe cyane,<ref>https://igihe.com/imyidagaduro/gospel/article/liza-kamikazi-yakoze-indirimbo-ifite-umwihariko-mu-rugendo-rw-umuziki-amazemo</ref> Liza afatanya ubuhanzi n'itangazamakuru aho akora kuri televisiyo y'u Rwanda  agakora ikiganiro cya gikiristitu kitwa " umutima ku mutima" ( Heart to Heart).<ref>https://inyarwanda.com/inkuru/108010/liza-kamikazi-agiye-gutangira-gukora-kuri-televiziyo-yu-rwanda-108010.html</ref>

